<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>看房評分資料庫 (自2026.07)</title>
    <style>
        /* ================= 基礎變數與設計系統 ================= */
        :root {
            --bg-main: #0B1120; --bg-panel: #1E293B; --bg-panel-hover: #334155; 
            --primary: #3B82F6; --primary-hover: #2563EB; --text-main: #F8FAFC; 
            --text-muted: #94A3B8; --border: #334155; 
            --success: #10B981; --danger: #EF4444; --warning: #F59E0B;
            --nav-height: 60px;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg-main); color: var(--text-main); line-height: 1.5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }

        /* ================= 導覽列與視圖 ================= */
        nav { position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; height: var(--nav-height); background-color: var(--bg-panel); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 1rem; z-index: 1000; justify-content: space-between; overflow-x: auto; white-space: nowrap;}
        .nav-brand { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0; margin-right: 1rem; color: var(--text-main);}
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; }
        .nav-btn { background: transparent; border: none; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; transition: 0.2s; min-height: 40px;}
        .nav-btn:hover { color: var(--text-main); background-color: var(--bg-panel-hover); }
        .nav-btn.active { color: var(--primary); background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); font-weight: bold; }
        
        main { margin-top: var(--nav-height); padding: 2rem 1rem; max-width: 1200px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; word-break: break-word; }
        .view-section { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
        .view-section.active { display: block; }
        .page-header { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;}
        .page-title { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 600; }
        .page-subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

        /* ================= 元件 ================= */
        .btn { padding: 0.6rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; border: none; font-size: 0.95rem; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; font-weight: 500; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem; min-height: 44px; }
        .btn-primary { background-color: var(--primary); color: white; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: var(--primary-hover); }
        .btn-success { background-color: var(--success); color: white; }
        .btn-warning { background-color: var(--warning); color: #000; }
        .btn-danger { background-color: var(--danger); color: white; }
        .btn-outline { background-color: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-main); }
        .btn-sm { padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem; font-size: 0.85rem; min-height: 36px; }
        .btn-huge { padding: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; border-radius: 8px; width: 100%; font-weight: bold; }

        .form-section { background-color: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .form-section-title { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary); border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;}
        .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
        .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
        .form-group.full-width { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
        label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 500; }
        input[type="text"], input[type="number"], select, textarea { width: 100%; padding: 0.8rem; background-color: var(--bg-main); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; color: var(--text-main); font-size: 1rem; }
        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); }
        textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; line-height: 1.5;}
        
        .checkbox-group { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.5rem 0;}
        .checkbox-group input { width: 24px; height: 24px; cursor: pointer;}
        .auto-calc-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; } .auto-calc-wrapper input { flex: 1; }
        .btn-reset-auto { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--warning); border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.6rem; display: none; font-size: 0.8rem;}
        .is-manual .btn-reset-auto { display: block; }

        /* ================= 列表與卡片 ================= */
        .list-controls { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: var(--bg-panel); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);}
        .house-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4rem;}
        .house-card { background-color: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; transition: transform 0.2s; position:relative;}
        .house-card.shortlist { border-color: var(--warning); box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2); }
        .card-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.75rem;}
        .card-title { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;}
        .badge { font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 99px; background: #334155; color: white; display: inline-block;}
        .card-body { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); flex: 1;}
        .data-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;}
        .data-val { color: var(--text-main); font-weight: 500;}
        .card-actions { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 1rem; align-items:center; flex-wrap: wrap;}
        .empty-state { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; background-color: var(--bg-panel); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px dashed var(--border); color: var(--text-muted); }

        /* ================= 評分看板 ================= */
        .score-banner { background-color: var(--danger); color: white; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: none; position: sticky; top: var(--nav-height); z-index: 900;}
        .score-dashboard { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; background: var(--bg-main); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .sd-box { text-align: center; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);}
        .sd-box-title { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
        .sd-box-value { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); }
        .sd-box-value.total { font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--success); }
        .sd-judgment { grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px dashed var(--border); color: var(--text-main);}
        .sc-item { background: var(--bg-main); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
        .sc-header { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem;}
        .sc-radios { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .sc-radios label { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; padding: 0.6rem; background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.95rem; flex: 1; min-width: 70px; justify-content: center;}
        .sc-radios label:hover { background: var(--bg-panel-hover); }
        .sc-radios input[type="radio"] { margin: 0; cursor: pointer; width: 18px; height: 18px;}
        .sc-tips { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px; border-left: 3px solid var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .flaw-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.8rem; padding-top:0.8rem; border-top: 1px dashed var(--border); font-size: 0.9rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;}

        /* ================= Dashboard 統計儀表板 ================= */
        .dash-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;}
        .dash-card { background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;}
        .dash-val { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); margin: 0.5rem 0;}
        .dash-label { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;}

        /* ================= 比較模式 ================= */
        .compare-bar { position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(5px); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 -4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); transform: translateY(100%); transition: transform 0.3s;}
        .compare-bar.show { transform: translateY(0); }
        .cmp-legend { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; flex-wrap: wrap;}
        .cmp-badge { padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; }
        .cmp-best { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.2); color: #34D399; }
        .cmp-worst { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.2); color: #F87171; }
        .compare-desktop { overflow-x: auto; background: var(--bg-panel); border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; min-width: 800px; }
        .compare-table th, .compare-table td { border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0.8rem; text-align: center; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .compare-table th { background: var(--bg-panel-hover); color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: normal; position: sticky; left: 0; z-index: 10; width: 120px;}
        .compare-table .house-head { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); background: var(--bg-panel); position: static; width: auto;}
        .val-best { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1); color: #34D399; font-weight: bold; }
        .val-worst { background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1); color: #F87171; text-decoration: underline; }
        .val-warn { color: var(--warning); font-weight: bold; }
        .compare-mobile { display: none; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
        .cmp-m-card { background: var(--bg-panel); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; }
        .cmp-m-title { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align:center;}
        .cmp-m-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0.6rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); align-items:flex-start; gap:1rem;}
        .cmp-m-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .cmp-m-label { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; flex-shrink: 0;}
        .cmp-m-val { text-align: right; font-size: 0.95rem; word-break: break-word;}

        /* ================= 現場看房 Overlay ================= */
        .insp-overlay { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: var(--bg-main); z-index: 2000; display: none; flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto;}
        .insp-overlay.active { display: flex; }
        .insp-header { padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-panel); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;}
        .insp-progress-bar { height: 8px; background: var(--bg-main); border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 0.5rem; overflow: hidden; }
        .insp-progress-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--success); width: 0%; transition: width 0.3s; }
        .insp-header-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;}
        .insp-body { padding: 1.5rem 1rem; flex: 1; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;}
        .insp-step-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.4;}
        .insp-status-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .insp-status-btn { padding: 1rem 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-panel); color: var(--text-main); cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; min-height: 60px;}
        .insp-status-btn.active { border-color: var(--primary); background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); }
        .insp-status-btn.s-good.active { border-color: var(--success); background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); }
        .insp-status-btn.s-poor.active { border-color: var(--warning); background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2); }
        .insp-status-btn.s-flaw { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
        .insp-status-btn.s-flaw.active { border-color: var(--danger); background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2); color: #F87171;}
        .insp-reinspect-box { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--warning); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; cursor:pointer;}
        .insp-reinspect-box input { width: 28px; height: 28px; accent-color: var(--warning); pointer-events: none;}
        .insp-reinspect-box label { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: bold; color: var(--warning); margin: 0; pointer-events: none;}
        .insp-footer { padding: 1rem; background: var(--bg-panel); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; gap: 1rem; position: sticky; bottom: 0; flex-wrap: wrap;}
        .summary-card { background: var(--bg-panel); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); }
        .summary-card.danger { border-left-color: var(--danger); }
        .summary-card.warning { border-left-color: var(--warning); }
        .summary-list { margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-main); font-size: 0.95rem;}

        /* ================= 設定與備份專用 ================= */
        .settings-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-main); border-radius: 6px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;}
        .alert-box { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1rem;}
        input[type="file"] { display: none; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-brand { display:none; } .nav-links { width: 100%; justify-content: space-between; overflow-x: auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;}
            .compare-desktop { display: none; }
            .compare-mobile { display: flex; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav id="main-nav">
        <div class="nav-brand">看房評分庫 (自2026.07)</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <button class="nav-btn" data-target="view-dashboard" onclick="app.switchView('view-dashboard')">總覽</button>
            <button class="nav-btn active" data-target="view-list" onclick="app.switchView('view-list')">列表</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" data-target="view-form" onclick="app.createNew()">+ 新增</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" data-target="view-compare" onclick="app.switchView('view-compare')" style="display:none;" id="nav-btn-compare">比較</button>
            <button class="nav-btn" data-target="view-settings" onclick="app.switchView('view-settings')">⚙️ 設定</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Dashboard 視圖 -->
        <section id="view-dashboard" class="view-section">
            <div class="page-header"><div><h1 class="page-title">總覽 Dashboard</h1></div></div>
            <div class="dash-stats" id="dash-stats-container">
                <!-- 由 JS 動態繪製統計 -->
            </div>
            <div class="form-section" style="border-color: var(--primary);">
                <div class="form-section-title">快速入門</div>
                <p style="color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1rem;">歡迎使用！本系統完全離線運行，所有資料保存在您的瀏覽器中。第一次使用建議載入示範資料進行體驗。</p>
                <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="app.generateDemoData()">📥 載入示範物件</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 物件列表視圖 -->
        <section id="view-list" class="view-section active">
            <div class="page-header">
                <div><h1 class="page-title">物件列表</h1><div class="page-subtitle" id="list-subtitle"></div></div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="app.createNew()">+ 新增紀錄</button>
            </div>
            <div class="list-controls">
                <input type="text" id="filter-search" placeholder="搜尋建案名稱..." oninput="app.renderList()">
                <select id="filter-status" onchange="app.renderList()"><option value="">所有狀態</option></select>
                <select id="sort-by" onchange="app.renderList()">
                    <option value="updatedAt-desc">更新時間 (新到舊)</option>
                    <option value="scoreTotal-desc">綜合總分 (高到低)</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div id="list-container" class="house-grid"></div>
        </section>

        <!-- 浮動比較工具列 -->
        <div id="compare-bar" class="compare-bar">
            <div>已選 <span id="cmp-count" style="color:var(--primary); font-weight:bold; font-size:1.2rem;">0</span>/4 筆</div>
            <button class="btn btn-success" onclick="app.switchView('view-compare')">📊 比較</button>
            <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" onclick="app.clearCompare()">清除</button>
        </div>

        <!-- 比較視圖 -->
        <section id="view-compare" class="view-section">
            <div class="page-header">
                <div><h1 class="page-title">物件比較與決策</h1><div class="page-subtitle">支援最多4筆物件橫向對比。</div></div>
                <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="app.switchView('view-list')">返回</button>
            </div>
            <div class="cmp-legend">
                <span class="cmp-badge cmp-best">綠色：最佳/最高值</span>
                <span class="cmp-badge cmp-worst">紅色：最差/最低值</span>
                <span style="color:var(--warning); font-weight:bold;">⚠️ 待確認或硬傷警示</span>
            </div>
            <div class="compare-desktop" id="cmp-desktop-container"></div>
            <div class="compare-mobile" id="cmp-mobile-container"></div>
        </section>

        <!-- 表單視圖 -->
        <section id="view-form" class="view-section">
            <div id="elimination-banner" class="score-banner">🚨 警告：本物件存在直接淘汰硬傷，分數僅供參考！</div>
            <div class="page-header">
                <div><h1 class="page-title" id="form-title">新增/編輯物件</h1></div>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem;">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="app.switchView('view-list')">取消</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="app.saveHouse()">儲存</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <form id="house-form" oninput="app.handleFormInput()">
                <input type="hidden" id="f_id" name="id">
                <div class="form-section">
                    <div class="form-section-title">基礎資料</div>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="form-group"><label>建案名稱 *</label><input type="text" name="projectName" required></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>行政區</label><input type="text" name="district"></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>看房狀態</label><select name="status" id="f_status"></select></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>房屋類型</label><select name="propertyType"><option value="預售屋">預售屋</option><option value="新成屋">新成屋</option><option value="中古屋">中古屋</option></select></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>房型 (例: 3房2廳)</label><input type="text" name="pattern"></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>總價 (萬)</label><input type="number" name="priceTotal" min="0" step="0.1"></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>單價 (萬/坪)</label><input type="number" name="priceUnit" min="0" step="0.1"></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>權狀坪數 *</label><input type="number" name="pingTotal" class="trigger-calc" min="0" step="0.01" required></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label>室內坪數</label><input type="number" name="pingUsable" class="trigger-calc" min="0" step="0.01"></div>
                        <div class="form-group calc-field"><label>室內使用率 (%) [自動]</label><div class="auto-calc-wrapper"><input type="number" name="ratioUsable" data-calc="ratioUsable" step="0.1"><button type="button" class="btn-reset-auto" onclick="app.resetAutoCalc('ratioUsable')">↺</button></div></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-section" style="border-color: var(--primary);">
                    <div class="score-dashboard">
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">暫定總分</div><div class="sd-box-value total" id="sd_total">0.0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">房屋(50)</div><div class="sd-box-value" id="sd_house">0.0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">社區(25)</div><div class="sd-box-value" id="sd_comm">0.0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">環境(25)</div><div class="sd-box-value" id="sd_env">0.0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">完成度</div><div class="sd-box-value" id="sd_completion">0%</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">待確認</div><div class="sd-box-value warning" id="sd_tbc">0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-box"><div class="sd-box-title">硬傷數</div><div class="sd-box-value danger" id="sd_flaws">0</div></div>
                        <div class="sd-judgment" id="sd_judgment_text">尚未評估</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <details class="form-section"><summary class="form-section-title" style="cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:0;">一、房屋本體評分 (50分) 展開</summary><div id="container-house-scores" style="margin-top:1rem;"></div></details>
                <details class="form-section"><summary class="form-section-title" style="cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:0;">二、社區條件評分 (25分) 展開</summary><div id="container-comm-scores" style="margin-top:1rem;"></div></details>
                <details class="form-section"><summary class="form-section-title" style="cursor:pointer; margin-bottom:0;">三、周邊環境評分 (25分) 展開</summary><div id="container-env-scores" style="margin-top:1rem;"></div></details>

                <div class="form-section" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);">
                    <div class="form-section-title">四、決策摘要與紀錄 <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" onclick="app.autoSuggestSummary()">🤖 自動擷取</button></div>
                    <div class="form-grid">
                        <div class="form-group full-width"><label>👍 優點</label><textarea name="notesPros" id="notesPros"></textarea></div>
                        <div class="form-group full-width"><label>👎 缺點</label><textarea name="notesCons" id="notesCons"></textarea></div>
                        <div class="form-group full-width"><label>☠️ 硬傷/最大風險</label><textarea name="notesRisks" id="notesRisks"></textarea></div>
                        <div class="form-group full-width"><label>❓ 待確認/複看事項</label><textarea name="notesPending" id="notesPending"></textarea></div>
                        <div class="form-group checkbox-group" style="padding:1rem; background:var(--bg-main); border-radius:8px; margin-top:0.5rem; width:100%;">
                            <input type="checkbox" name="isShortlisted" id="f_shortlist">
                            <label for="f_shortlist" style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--warning); font-size:1.1rem; flex:1;">⭐ 列入決選</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: right; padding-bottom: 2rem;"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-right: 1rem;" onclick="app.cancelEdit()">取消</button><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="app.saveHouse()">儲存紀錄</button></div>
            </form>
        </section>

        <!-- 設定與備份視圖 -->
        <section id="view-settings" class="view-section">
            <div class="page-header"><div><h1 class="page-title">⚙️ 備份與跨裝置交接</h1><div class="page-subtitle">匯出 JSON 保護資料，並產生 CSV 報表。</div></div></div>
            
            <div class="form-section">
                <div class="form-section-title">💾 備份與合併機制</div>
                <div class="settings-card">
                    <h3>1. 匯出備份 (JSON)</h3>
                    <p>將所有看房紀錄完整打包下載。</p>
                    <div id="backup-status-ui" style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-weight:bold;"></div>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="app.exportJSON()">📥 匯出資料庫</button>
                </div>
                <div class="settings-card">
                    <h3>2. 匯入與合併 (Merge)</h3>
                    <p>選擇先前的 JSON，系統會依修改時間自動合併最新進度。</p>
                    <label for="import-json" class="btn btn-success" style="cursor:pointer; display:inline-flex;">📂 選擇 JSON 檔案</label>
                    <input type="file" id="import-json" accept=".json,application/json" onchange="app.handleImportJSON(event)">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-section">
                <div class="form-section-title">📊 報表與匯出</div>
                <div class="settings-card" style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="app.exportCSV('all')">匯出全部物件 CSV</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="app.exportCSV('compare')">匯出比較中物件 CSV</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-section" style="border-color: var(--danger);">
                <div class="form-section-title" style="color: var(--danger);">⚠️ 危險區域</div>
                <button class="btn btn-danger" onclick="app.clearAllData()">🗑️ 刪除全部資料庫</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- 現場看房 Overlay -->
    <div id="insp-overlay" class="insp-overlay">
        <div id="insp-view-setup" style="display: none; padding: 2rem 1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; width:100%;">
            <h1 class="page-title" style="margin-bottom:2rem; text-align:center;">📱 現場看房模式</h1>
            <div class="form-section">
                <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><label>正在檢視：</label><div id="insp-setup-name" style="font-size:1.4rem; color:var(--primary); font-weight:bold;"></div></div>
                <div class="form-group" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;"><label>情境：</label><select id="insp-setup-mode" style="font-size: 1.2rem;"><option value="初次看房">初次看房</option><option value="白天複看">白天複看</option><option value="晚上複看">晚上複看</option><option value="雨天複看">雨天複看</option></select></div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-huge" onclick="insp.startRun()">🚀 開始檢查</button>
                <button class="btn btn-outline btn-huge" style="margin-top:1rem;" onclick="insp.close()">取消</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="insp-view-run" style="display: none; flex-direction: column; height: 100%;">
            <div class="insp-header">
                <div class="insp-header-top"><span style="font-weight:bold;" id="insp-step-counter"></span><button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline" onclick="insp.abort()">退出</button></div>
                <div class="insp-progress-bar"><div class="insp-progress-fill" id="insp-progress"></div></div>
