            <h1 class="page-title" style="text-align:center;">🎉 檢查完成</h1>
            <div style="text-align:center; color:var(--text-muted); margin-bottom:2rem;" id="insp-sum-meta"></div>
            <div class="summary-card"><div style="font-weight:bold; color:var(--primary);">📊 完成度：<span id="insp-sum-rate"></span></div></div>
            <div class="form-section" style="margin-top:2rem;"><p>將紀錄彙整至正式「決策摘要」？</p><button class="btn btn-success btn-huge" onclick="insp.mergeToHouse()">📝 確認合併</button><button class="btn btn-outline btn-huge" style="margin-top:1rem;" onclick="insp.close()">放棄</button></div>
        </div>
